divs: Sighting Details( San Diego Ca, October 5, 2012 ) ��� Me and My Friends were just hanging out in their backyard around 9:00 when we saw this very big UFO go over us it had skimed the tree and when it was over us it Made a red line go down the yard . We think it might had said some thing, later that night we were all in the front yard ( it was about 9:30 now ) and we saw it again, but this time my friend and I saw a green Mist. We ended up tring to see if we saw and more We did we went all around the nabor hood. And the whole time their was some thing in the sky Following us .The Thing in the Sky was a UFO it Had redish , Blackish, Gray Gold Back lights the bottom was Gray with little hoverers on the bottom the UFO was Gray and black.
